We indicated that the rationale supporting the applicability, emission limitations, monitoring, recordkeeping, reporting, and other provisions for each of the six federal rules is found in the preambles and background documents 

for those rulemakings. The six federal rules are available on the Electronic Code of Federal Regulations at: 
